Package: Rthreads
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Norm Matloff <normmatloff@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Norm Matloff <normmatloff@gmail.com>
Date: 2025-05-29
Title: Parallel Threads Environment for R
Description: Provides a threads-type parallel programming environment for R.
   The package gives the R programmer the clearer, more concise
   shared memory world view, and typically gives superior
   performance as well.  
OS_type: unix
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: bigmemory (>= 4.0.0), parallel,synchronicity
Suggests: knitr,rmarkdown
LazyLoad: no
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL (>= 2)
